                            <comment id="15159023" author="blerer" created="Tue, 23 Feb 2016 15:11:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;AbstractQueryPager&lt;/tt&gt; was not taking into account the fact that for tables with no clustering columns there is only one row per partition. When the next page was fetched, the pager was believing that it still had to return some rows from the partition.&lt;/p&gt;

